rComments: Professor Burke is one my favourite professors at Rotman. He is very knowledgable on the course material and wants to see people succeed. Since he is such a recent graduate of Rotman, he knows what it's like to be a student and provides lots of advice. He can also be very funny. He grades fairly and attending class is CRUCIAL to succeeding.
Amazing Professor! He makes every class very interesting with funny memes :) He's also very fair.

Teaches lectures to understand content so not only are you able to mechanically do questions, but you can relate it to the world today.   Great prof who offers loads of office hours, and ensures you understand the content.
favourite rotman prof by far! he cared about his students and would book the classroom after the lecture for students who needed extra help. plus HE CUTE
Best Rotman prof EVER. I like how he did old exam examples in class and was funny, seemed like he actually cared about us. Class is really hard though.
Amazing lectures and office hours, wish he was teaching RSM333
Amazing lecturer. The material is tough and can be dry, but he makes it more exciting. Would love to take another class with him!
